"{\"uid\": \"rappler.com-sports-south-sudan-brushes-off-anthem-blunder-win-basketball-debut-paris-olympics-2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  SUMMARY  This is AI generated summarization, which may have errors.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 69, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19, \"end\": 21, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.9914499651657296, \"rank\": 0.008623766833150241, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For context, always refer to the full article.\", \"from\": 70, \"to\": 116, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"HURDLING OBSTACLES.\", \"from\": 118, \"to\": 137, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The South Sudan men's basketball team celebrates after winning the match against Puerto Rico.\", \"from\": 138, \"to\": 231, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 219, \"end\": 230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico\", \"score\": 0.9953693508636533, \"rank\": 0.0035825897164417815, \"text\": \"Puerto Rico\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reuters  PARIS, France - South Sudan brushed off an anthem blunder by the Paris Games organizers on Sunday, July 28, and bounced back in style to earn their first men's basketball victory on their Olympic debut with a convincing 90-79 Group C opening win over Puerto Rico.\", \"from\": 233, \"to\": 505, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 233, \"end\": 240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 0.99999999997749, \"rank\": 2.2459502081110807e-11, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}, {\"begin\": 249, \"end\": 255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.928244254134709, \"rank\": 0.06884038215294587, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 493, \"end\": 504, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico\", \"score\": 0.9953693508636533, \"rank\": 0.0035825897164417815, \"text\": \"Puerto Rico\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Before their win, the organizers inadvertently played the anthem of neighboring Sudan - and later apologized for the mistake.\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 632, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 587, \"end\": 592, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sudan\", \"score\": 0.9999999804435904, \"rank\": 1.6227035547215943e-08, \"text\": \"Sudan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sudan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sudan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The incident came just a couple of days afterSouth Koreawas introduced as from rival North Korea\\u00a0during the opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 634, \"to\": 759, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 719, \"end\": 730, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Korea_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6675656093176132, \"rank\": 0.49790862122595475, \"text\": \"North Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Korea_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Korea_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The announcer introduced them as the \\\"Democratic People's Republic of Korea\\\" - the official name of North Korea - in French and English.\", \"from\": 760, \"to\": 896, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 860, \"end\": 871, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Korea_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6675656093176132, \"rank\": 0.49790862122595475, \"text\": \"North Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Korea_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Korea_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 877, \"end\": 883, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8673601630642886, \"rank\": 0.07793168631223714, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"South Sudan gained independence from Sudan after a referendum in 2011 but disputes over borders, natural resources and political power have continued to spark violent clashes between the two.\", \"from\": 898, \"to\": 1089, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 935, \"end\": 940, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sudan\", \"score\": 0.9999999804435904, \"rank\": 1.6227035547215943e-08, \"text\": \"Sudan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sudan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sudan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fans quickly expressed their frustration, with one proudly waving the South Sudan flag and shouting until the wrong anthem was stopped.\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1226, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The \\\"Bright Stars,\\\" as Sudan's basketball team is known, have become Olympic battlers thanks to the work of former NBA All-Star Luol Deng, who has been president of the country's basketball federation since 2019.\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1440, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1251, \"end\": 1256, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sudan\", \"score\": 0.9999999804435904, \"rank\": 1.6227035547215943e-08, \"text\": \"Sudan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sudan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sudan\"}, {\"begin\": 1343, \"end\": 1355, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBA_All-Star_Game\", \"score\": 0.99994714196219, \"rank\": 5.2851171947909456e-05, \"text\": \"NBA All-Star\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBA_All-Star_Game\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBA_All-Star_Game\"}, {\"begin\": 1356, \"end\": 1365, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luol_Deng\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Luol Deng\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luol_Deng\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luol_Deng\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"[This victory] means everything,\\\" said forward Wenyen Gabriel after their historic Olympic basketball triumph.\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1553, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1490, \"end\": 1504, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wenyen_Gabriel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Wenyen Gabriel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wenyen_Gabriel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wenyen_Gabriel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a unifying moment.\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1578, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are all united now through basketball and it's proof of what sport can do for a country,\\\"  \\\"I think it means the world for our country.\", \"from\": 1579, \"to\": 1717, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It just lets them know that anything is possible as long as you are willing to work hard and fight against adversity,\\\" added teammate Carlik Jones.\", \"from\": 1718, \"to\": 1865, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1852, \"end\": 1864, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlik_Jones\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlik Jones\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlik_Jones\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlik_Jones\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Enthusiastic fans recognized the importance of the debut victory, with Esther Soma having traveled from South Sudan just for the game.\", \"from\": 1867, \"to\": 2001, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1938, \"end\": 1944, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Esther\", \"score\": 0.9994702779249494, \"rank\": 0.0005298654450794359, \"text\": \"Esther\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Esther\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Esther\"}, {\"begin\": 1945, \"end\": 1949, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chandra\", \"score\": 0.9682556863196816, \"rank\": 0.03278422965153324, \"text\": \"Soma\", \"types\": [\"Q24229398\", \"Q178885\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chandra\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chandra\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is bigger than basketball for us.\", \"from\": 2003, \"to\": 2042, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The fact that they are here at the Olympics in this stadium is already the biggest thing,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2143, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Deng brought in American former NBA player Royal Ivey as head coach.\", \"from\": 2145, \"to\": 2213, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2145, \"end\": 2149, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deng_Xiaoping\", \"score\": 0.963364592135053, \"rank\": 0.03802860050774622, \"text\": \"Deng\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deng_Xiaoping\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deng_Xiaoping\"}, {\"begin\": 2161, \"end\": 2169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999957257835317, \"rank\": 2.0084403457207927e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2177, \"end\": 2180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 0.9999999995118287, \"rank\": 4.765720218028446e-10, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 2188, \"end\": 2198, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Ivey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Royal Ivey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Ivey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Ivey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ivey said they would keep on battling.\", \"from\": 2214, \"to\": 2252, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is great for a country that's been through so much war, so much trouble, to come together through sports is a great achievement, we are going to keep going,\\\" he said after the victory.\", \"from\": 2254, \"to\": 2444, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Captain Kuany Kuany's brother Akok also hailed the milestone win, having traveled with his whole family from Melbourne, Australia, to celebrate the team's success.\", \"from\": 2446, \"to\": 2609, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2476, \"end\": 2480, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akok\", \"score\": 0.9999999993651727, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Akok\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akok\"}, {\"begin\": 2555, \"end\": 2564, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"score\": 0.7971535372231286, \"rank\": 0.21156968744237573, \"text\": \"Melbourne\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\"}, {\"begin\": 2566, \"end\": 2575, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_na